            </span-->

            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>I guess I’ve had a lifetime love of chocolate. The older I get, the more powerful it becomes. I really do like chocolate: milk chocolate. I don’t care for the dark chocolate, even though they tell me dark chocolate is healthy for you. I prefer the wicked milk chocolate. My family tolerates me and they often feed my habit, giving me gifts of chocolate.
            </span>

