            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>I need a lot of help getting through most of my days now. I have found that thoughts, just different thoughts that I hear and I read and I’ve listened to, they mean a lot to me and they help me a great deal, so I usually type them up on the computer, print them off, put them on a little tag, and hang ‘em up where I can see them and read them. They help me a lot and I’ll share some of those with you.


